17:32.585 --> 17:34.621
* And you had a doo-wack...

17:34.654 --> 17:37.257
[Hope cooing]

17:37.290 --> 17:39.292
* You got money in the sack

17:39.326 --> 17:41.861
* Both hands on the wheel
and your shoulders right back *

17:41.894 --> 17:43.763
* Root, doo, doo, doo,
